OL,5, More than two thirds of the UK's 22    
OL,6, busiest airports have introduced or    
OL,7, increased charges for drivers to drop  
OL,8, off passengers since the start of the  
OL,9, pandemic, the RAC says.                
OL,11,FStansted charges the most of drop-offs,
OL,12,Fwhile London City is free and Belfast  
OL,13,Fand Cardiff are free for set amounts of
OL,14,Ftime, the motoring group says.         
OL,16,FSixteen of the 22 airports analysed    
OL,17,Fintroduced or increased the charges.   
OL,19,FThe RAC said it appeared airports were 
OL,20,Ftrying to recoup pandemic losses.      
